    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>What about overriding the method with</p>\n\n<pre><code>void f(int value)\n{\n  f((byte)value);\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>this will allow for <code>f(0)</code></p>\n"
