    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>If you're passing literals in code, what's stopping you from simply declaring it ahead of time?</p>\n\n<pre><code>byte b = 0; //Set to desired value.\nf(b);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
